00:00:44.730 --> 00:00:45.688
If caught early

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:47.080
and the toe is still flexible,

00:00:47.080 --> 00:00:48.456
hammer toe may be treated

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:50.104
by wearing roomier footwear.

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:51.576
Once the toe is rigid,

00:00:51.570 --> 00:00:53.416
surgery may be needed to straighten it

00:00:53.410 --> 00:00:54.568
by cutting the tendon

00:00:54.560 --> 00:00:56.912
and sometimes removing pieces of bone.

